      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments performed on the same FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under overlapping operating conditions (flow rate 2–8 L/min, speed 2000–3500 RPM).",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experiments use identical pump geometry and bovine blood analog. Operating envelope covers the CPB clinical range. Validation activities are directly relevant to the intended simulation use. Required level 2 achieved."
