      "rationale": "SST k-omega is widely validated for rotating turbomachinery flows. Giersiepen power-law hemolysis model is standard for CFD hemolysis at this scale. Literature supports model-form adequacy. Formal UQ not required at MRL 2; level 2 accepted via expert judgment."
