      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Equivalency between validation experiment inputs and COU inputs reviewed qualitatively; quantitative equivalency mapping not required at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Validation operating conditions (2–8 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM) bracket the CPB clinical operating range. Geometric equivalency is exact (same FDA generic pump). Qualitative equivalency sufficient at MRL 2 level 1."
