    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 requirements table permitting reduced rigor for lower-risk model uses. Output comparison (factor 5) exceeds requirements at level 3. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in the CPB context as described in the bound requirement and claim documentation. Decision: Accepted.",
